```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant D as Domain Team PR
  participant CI as CI/CD
  participant GOV as Governance Rules
  participant CAT as Catalog/Metadata
  participant PLAT as Platform

  D->>CI: Submit data product change (contract + models)
  CI->>GOV: Validate contract, PII tags, naming, tests
  alt passes
    CI->>PLAT: Deploy pipeline + publish artifacts
    PLAT->>CAT: Register dataset + lineage + owner
  else fails
    CI-->>D: Block merge with actionable errors
  end
```
